  </must-convey>
  <hook-questions>
    - What are these new plant creatures?
    - Did it just... talk?
    - Why are they speaking corporate jargon?
    - Can they actually help her?
    - Will she survive this absurdity?
  </hook-questions>
  <launching-situation>
    Kira standing alone after Scout left, hearing more plant creatures approaching through the trees
  </launching-situation>
  <location-impression>
    Purple forest, other plants emerging from trees and undergrowth, fruiting body sprouting from ground
  </location-impression>
